( 10... Qc1 $143 { t } 11. cxd4 12... exd4 13. Nc6 14... c3 15. Bf5 $15 {[%cal Ge7e6,Gh7h6,Gf8e7,Ge8g8,Rb7b5,Rb5b4]} {  Black has a much better version of the Caro-Exchange. You want to play...e6-h6-Be7-0-0 next. } )
( 10... b3 $143 { t creates a lot of unnecessary holes on the Queenside. After } 11. cxd4 12... exd4 13. Bg4 $11 {[%csl Ra2,Rc2,Rc3]} {[%cal Gb8c6,Ge7e6,Ga8c8]} {  Black has managed to solve all of their opening problems. } )
